<item>
            <title>[FLINK-1756] Rename Stream Monitoring to Stream Checkpointing</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-1756</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently, to enable the streaming checkpointing, you have to set &quot;monitoring&quot; on. I vote to call it &quot;checkpointing&quot;, because that describes it better and is more intuitive.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12783548">FLINK-1756</key>
